# PITEST

> An object oriented testing framework.

## Features

- Dynamic argument passing.

- Dependency tracking among tests.

- Namespacing when discovering test cases.

## Code Samples

Please refer to `code-samples/` for usage examples.

## Documentation

- Formal documentation on the API and expected usage is yet to be done.

- A complete documentation of the scheduler used by pitest is

    ./doc/scheduler.md

## Unit Tests

Unit tests are available under `unittests/`.
